summary: Maximum Polygons, Maximum Smoothness, Maximum Collisions, & Maximum Jiggles!
descriptionHtml:
Okay, so the original got taken down, but it's for the best. I've become motivated to do an entirely new and original body. There is a poll in the posts to decide which texture the NEW Maximum Body will use. Please vote :)

Have a great day and come back for updates!




And yes, we are about to alpha (yay!) but that's okay because I have some new techniques I picked up while working on my hdt hair project that I think will make this turn out even better than before!
author: RedKnight
